A LYCORIS Locon of Sophie Twilight from the Anime/Manga series, Tonari no Kyuuketsuki-san. You will have to install this extension made by KohakuBlueLeaf into your webui to fully use a Locon LORAs

https://github.com/KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon

This Locon was made with a collection of fanart images and anime screencaps from the show, she can be easily changed into multiple outfits and hairstyles like was shown off in the series whenever a part of her hair was turned to ash or her beautiful grey hair was played around like a doll's hair. She's very cute for a 360 year old otaku vampire

Compatibility

Trained on the NAI model, so it's pretty much compatible with ever NAI based Anime model mix that you can find on the internet

Recommended Weight

Always 1.0 by itself and 0.8-0.7 if you're mixing it with other LORAs.

Trigger Tokens

normsophie will be the token needed for her normal look, you may want to up the strength on some additional tags because even when I tried correcting the tags given to her training images and used multiple network ranks and learning rates there is some rng where her outfit will be a full on black one but as long as if you use

"very long hair, black dress, hair between eyes, white sailor collar, brooch, red ribbon, black pantyhose, tress ribbon, black tress ribbon, sidelocks, grey hair, red eyes"

you'll get her main look, not sure if it was the fanart look some people had with her outfit conflicting with the anime data that caused this but otherwise you'll get her main look 90% of the time

altsophie will be the token you use to allow for alternative outfits and hairstyles a lot more easier, if you notice one of her main outfit's clothing appearing in your outputs ensure you put one of the main tags from her main look into the negatives, didn't happen with my outputs but if it does there you go
